{"arkId":"cl020015633","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl020015633","modified ":"2025-08-19","title":"Une all\u00e9e dans un sous-bois","titleComplement":null,"denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Une all\u00e9e dans un sous-bois"}],"displayDateCreated":"","currentLocation":"Petit format","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[],"creator":[{"label":"Delacroix, Eug\u00e8ne","attributionLevel":"attribution actuelle","linkType":"original","dates":[{"date":"1863","place":"Paris","type":"date 2"},{"date":"1798","place":"Charenton-Saint-Maurice (Val-de-Marne)","type":"date 1"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q33477"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 3412, Recto","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"vol.20, p.99","type":"R\u00e9f\u00e9rence de l\u0027inventaire manuscrit"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Arts graphiques","printsDrawingsEntity":"Cabinet des dessins","printsDrawingsCollection":"Fonds des dessins et miniatures","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"0.22","displayDimension":"0.22 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"\u00e0 la feuille","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":"","note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0.2","displayDimension":"0.2 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"\u00e0 la feuille","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":"","note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Etat de conservation de l\u0027oeuvre (A. de la Chapelle, 9.02.2021)\nLes valeurs sombres de la technique sont recouvertes d\u0027un glacis transparent, vraisemblablement de la gomme arabique. Examin\u00e9 sous binoculaire, ce glacis se r\u00e9v\u00e8le syst\u00e9matiquement fissur\u00e9, mais \u00e9galement craquel\u00e9 dans de tr\u00e8s nombreuses zones. Les craquelures sont profondes, parfois disjointes et ont conduit \u00e7\u00e0 et l\u00e0 \u00e0 de micro-pertes de mati\u00e8re, de taille encore petites ( pas de d\u00e9placage). Conclusion : La couche picturale est tr\u00e8s fragilis\u00e9e par un glacis fissur\u00e9 et craquel\u00e9, allant jusqu\u0027\u00e0 la perte de mati\u00e8re.\nLe d\u00e9placement de ce dessin doit \u00eatre envisag\u00e9 avec beaucoup de prudence. S\u0027il devait n\u00e9anmoins \u00eatre pr\u00eat\u00e9, un cadre climatique et un transport \u00e0 plat seraient indispensables","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Derni\u00e8re provenance : Moreau-N\u00e9laton, Etienne","note":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"startYear":1907,"endYear":null}]}],"ownedBy":"","heldBy":"","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"collection":[{"value":"Delacroix, Eug\u00e8ne"},{"value":"Moreau-N\u00e9laton, Etienne"},{"value":"Meurice, Paul"}],"technic":[{"value":"papier beige"},{"value":"vernis"},{"value":"aquarelle"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/01\/56\/33\/00\/AGO015633-000_PE.jpg","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/01\/56\/33\/00\/AGO015633-000_PE.jpg","copyright":"GrandPalaisRmn (Mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Michel Urtado","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/01\/56\/33\/00\/AGO015633-001_PE.jpg","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/01\/56\/33\/00\/AGO015633-001_PE.jpg","copyright":" GrandPalaisRmn","type":"Autre","position":1}]}